# Chapter 3 — Keras and Data Retrieval in TensorFlow 2

This chapter explains how to build neural network models using the three Keras
APIs and how to retrieve datasets efficiently in TensorFlow. All figures are
included in the same order as in the original textbook.

---

## 3.1 Keras model-building APIs

Keras offers three ways to build neural networks depending on architectural
complexity: the Sequential API, the Functional API, and the Sub-classing API.
Each method provides different flexibility and ease of use.

